data.description: This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem in Magnolia Park At Englewood is nestled on a great size lot and features a storm shelter in the backyard! The spacious kitchen is accentuated with a bar and stainless appliances. Experience warmth in the expansive living room equipped with a gas log fireplace and LVP flooring that extends to the formal dining. Retreat to the primary suite showcasing a tray ceiling, dual sinks, and two generous walk-in closets, complemented by a separate shower. The guest bedrooms are sizeable, accompanied by a guest bathroom and a roomy laundry space ensures convenience. The covered back patio offers a space for entertaining, complemented by a spacious fenced backyard that features a storm shelter. Meanwhile, the covered front porch provides a setting for relaxation.
